c52.poster.avif?t=1771997006\" width=978 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3938880/extras/516f39258657c2fb8116e9e04b587c52.webm?t=1771997006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3938880/extras/516f39258657c2fb8116e9e04b587c52.mp4?t=1771997006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作為國家機娘的戰爭機器，沒有情感只有殺戮，但她們卻有著前凸後翹的身材，尤其是看板娘「賽菈」，我懷疑高層一定有放入他們的性癖，不然也太不科學了吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身為機娘維修官和忠實粉絲，用精湛的技術闖過防火牆、塞入暗門，手把手讓機娘們成為色色的樣子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3938880/extras/998204c2f831813501c2e60c5d044085.avif?t=1771997006\" width=978 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3938880/extras/15fbded586f39d1e3e705523e47a1f17.poster.avif?t=1771997006\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3938880/extras/15fbded586f39d1e3e705523e47a1f17.webm?t=1771997006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3938880/extras/15fbded586f39d1e3e705523e47a1f17.mp4?t=1771997006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>『探索蒐集零件，改造機娘讓她們更淫蕩！』</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索都市的街道，解決機娘們的需求並且獲得改裝晶片和零件，除發事件與機娘們培養關係，然後在維修的時候...嘿嘿嘿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>『就是現在！植入色色的程式！』</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在維修機娘的過程裡突入防火牆，推動色色代碼，埋入晶片中的漏洞，讓原本是戰爭機器的他們，成為性愛機器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ct